  propMaterialOverrides: []
  introLines:
  - Give me your lunch money or I'm telling my big brother!
  - This room is stupid and you look stupid too!
  answerWhatHappenedBefore: Someone said I didn't have the guts to put my tongue
    on the big frozen pole. I did it, got stuck, screamed for help, but everyone
    thought I was just throwing a tantrum
  answerWhatKindOfLife: A chaotic one. I ruled the sandbox with an iron fist and
    made sure nobody else got to use the good yellow plastic shovel
  answerWhatWasYourJob: I was the self-appointed king of the recess yard. I managed
    the black market trade of trading cards and juice boxes
  answerWhatHappenedClothes: My clothes are torn up because I got into three different
    fistfights during recess over a game of four-square
  answerWhyHaveItem: This baseball bat is my enforcement tool! I use it to smash
    sandcastles that other kids build without my permission
